node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Zero Skateboards on August 07, 2021 tagging @jamiethomas, @chriscobracole, @daneburman, @fosgraphics, and @tommysandoval_619.

node.text:
In 2003 @fosgraphics was a guest artist at Zero for a few months & made some amazing art including this ‘Living Dead’ series that came out in 2004.

We went back through his original sketch book & found some unused art in order to create boards for  @tommysandoval_619 & @daneburman

Thanks Fos for coming through 18 years later!🖤

These boards are on the site now & shipping to shops this coming week #linkinbio
